snippet.title: Amber Jelly Nails with Gems
snippet.description:
Suzie takes her Clear Gel with Under the Nail Design, and transforms them into beautiful two toned Jelly Nails adorned with Gems! 

Products used in this video:

Aluminix Chrome Gel by Joya Mia
http://bit.ly/2LSFRfk
Use the Coupon Code SUZIE for a 10% discount on anything in the Joya Mia Online store: http://bit.ly/joyamia
Suzie receives a commission if you use her Code, thank you for supporting her channel😘
